  "title" : "Eclipse: enable assertions",
  "body" : "<p>I'm running Eclipse Galileo. How do I enable assertions in Eclipse? </p>\n\n<p>As suggested by other sites, I've tried adding the arguments: <code>-ea</code>.  I have also tried changing the compiler compliance level to <code>1.4</code>. Neither of those suggestions worked. </p>\n"
